    "en": {
      "title": "A shooting in front of the Gampaha court",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to hospital sources, a shooting took place in front of the Gampaha court today (27) and four injured people have been admitted to the Gampaha District General Hospital.",
        "This shooting was done by someone or a group of people who came in a vehicle and a group of people who came with him for a hearing.",
        "Responding to a query that the four injured in the incident are currently receiving treatment in the intensive care unit of the Gampaha hospital, the hospital director, Dr. Saman Pathirana, said."
      ],
